							Founded in 2021, བོད་སྐད་སྙིང་པོ། (Tibetan at SINI) was born from a simple belief: learning Tibetan should be joyful, accessible, and focused on real communication. We started as a small community of passionate learners and have grown into a vibrant global family of Tibetan language enthusiasts.
						</p>
						<p>
							Our name, སྙིང་པོ། (SINI), means "heart" or "essence" in Tibetan - reflecting our commitment to getting to the heart of the language and creating a warm, supportive learning environment that feels like home.
						</p>
					</div>
